Say goodbye to the crashes!. Our team has been hard at work to ensure a smoother and bug free editing experience. No more interruptions while you re perfecting your pics! xoxo The Setty Team

New filters just dropped: 1995 Throwback Inspired by vintage film the 1995 filter adds a nostalgic summertime quality to any photo. The Throwback filter provides a more subtle film look bringing you back to you favorite summer memories. Try 1995 Throwback now! xoxo The Setty Team
